with version stable 2.28.4
with base    glib libXau popt
with also    --enable-static=no
with role    development
with trait   gnome library makej multilib-concurrent
with source  $GNOME_URL sources/libgtop/${VERSION:0:4}/libgtop-$VERSION.tar.xz
with info    home http://www.gnome.org/
with info    good 20120909
with info    last 20110830
with info    cite 'library for reporting system information
libgtop is a library that fetches information about the running
system such as cpu and memory usage, active processes etc.
On Linux systems, these information are taken directly from the
/proc filesystem while on other systems a server is used to read
those information from /dev/kmem or similar.'
